short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Write your tweets automatically with AI

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Finally grow your X account ! 

This extension adds several buttons on X.com in the reply section that lets you generate tweets automatically.

- All settings synced accros devices
- Key stored locally and encrypted
- Handles various tones of voice
- Also generates threads
